<i>especially my brother Barry.</i>

00:09.810 --> 00:11.143
<i>Basketball was his life.</i>

00:11.145 --> 00:13.345
Where's he gonna go?
Is he gonna go left?

00:13.347 --> 00:15.214
Is he gonna go right?
Hook!

00:15.216 --> 00:18.650
Oh, and he passes
to himself
off the backboard.

00:19.219 --> 00:21.120
Ah! Didn't count.

00:21.122 --> 00:21.987
(THUDS)

00:21.989 --> 00:23.722
Didn't count.

00:24.691 --> 00:25.858
He's on fire.

00:25.860 --> 00:27.026
You're bruising
the plums.

00:27.028 --> 00:29.895
What do you think
I'm made of,
fresh produce?

00:29.897 --> 00:31.196
<i>It was his passion.</i>

00:31.198 --> 00:32.731
Dr. J rejects him!
Barry!

00:32.733 --> 00:34.733
<i>He was obsessed.</i>
<i>It never stopped.</i>

00:34.735 --> 00:38.237
(CLATTERING)
Get that outta here!
Yeah!

00:38.239 --> 00:40.639
He backs him down.
He backs him down.

00:40.641 --> 00:42.274
<i>It was hard to live with.</i>

00:42.276 --> 00:43.776
You gotta get low!

00:43.778 --> 00:46.678
You gotta want it.
You can't come
in here soft.

00:46.680 --> 00:47.679
Gotta pee!

00:47.681 --> 00:49.715
(GRUNTING)
Move! I drank a big gulp!

00:49.717 --> 00:53.452
<i>My brother had one dream...</i>
<i>Going pro.</i>

00:53.454 --> 00:57.056
Three, two, one!

00:57.058 --> 00:58.791
At the buzzer!

00:58.793 --> 01:01.193
