left on the clock!

01:01.195 --> 01:02.428
He was misinformed!

01:02.430 --> 01:05.697
<i>Then he found a way</i>
<i>to make his dream a reality.</i>

01:05.699 --> 01:08.567
Mom, Dad,
I have huge news.

01:08.569 --> 01:10.602
If you'd follow me
outside to the hoop?

01:10.604 --> 01:11.737
No.
Here's good.

01:11.739 --> 01:15.207
What if I told you
one day there'd be
a piece of technology

01:15.209 --> 01:19.111
