professional basketball?

01:19.113 --> 01:21.113
Well, that day has come.

01:21.115 --> 01:22.548
(COMMERCIAL FANFARE PLAYING)
The Reebok Pump.

01:22.550 --> 01:24.116
A cushion of air
around the foot

01:24.118 --> 01:27.186
that literally allows you
to defy the laws of gravity.

01:27.188 --> 01:32.591
And the amazing part?
It's only $175.
Don't say no.

01:32.593 --> 01:33.459
No.
(MUSIC WARPS AND STOPS)

01:33.461 --> 01:37.796
Honey, I've got a pair
of Reeboks upstairs
you can have.

01:37.798 --> 01:38.664
Oh, really?

01:38.666 --> 01:40.699
Can I please borrow
your beige mom sneakers?

01:40.701 --> 01:45.537
Listen! My dream is to be
a basketball superstar,
not a nurse!

01:45.539 --> 01:48.941
Well, here's the thing
about your dream...

01:48.943 --> 01:50.042
It's stupid.

01:50.044 --> 01:50.909
You have the money.

01:50.911 --> 01:53.145
Just get your pants
and give it to me.

01:53.147 --> 01:55.981
Barry, your father's pants
are not a bank.

01:55.983 --> 01:58.283
Money comes from hard work,
you moron.

01:58.285 --> 01:59.551
You really want
those shoes,

01:59.553 --> 02:03.021
come down to the store
and work for 'em.

02:03.023 --> 02:05.691
Fine! But when I get
to the NBA,

02:05.693 --> 02:07.025
and you want
my autograph,

02:07.027 --> 02:12.097
I'm signing it,
"Worst wishes... Barry."

02:12.932 --> 02:13.866
<i>♪ I'm twisted up inside</i>

02:13.868 --> 02:18.670
<i>♪ But nonetheless</i>
<i>I feel the need to say</i>

02:20.240 --> 02:21.173
<i>♪ I don't know the future</i>

02:21.175 --> 02:25.677
<i>♪ But the past keeps getting</i>
<i>clearer every day ♪</i>

02:25.745 --> 02:28.480
ADULT ADAM:  <i>It was October 5,</i>
<i>1980-something,</i>

02:28.482 --> 02:30.415
<i>and while Barry pursued</i>
<i>his NBA dream,</i>

02:30.417 --> 02:32.784
<i>I pursued</i>
<i>a dream of my own...</i>

02:32.786 --> 02:34.386
<i>Seeing the movie</i>
Poltergeist.

02:34.388 --> 02:36.255
Please, please.
I'll do the dishes.

02:36.257 --> 02:38.824
