that ghost movie.

02:38.826 --> 02:39.625
It's too scary for you.

02:39.627 --> 02:42.594
Come on! It's re-released
at the Dollar Theater.

02:42.596 --> 02:45.230
A dollar!
You love a bargain.
(CHUCKLES)

02:45.232 --> 02:46.064
Forget it!

02:46.066 --> 02:49.168
