nephew saw that movie.

02:49.170 --> 02:52.871
Three days later,
he had a terror stroke.

02:53.273 --> 02:55.107
A terror stroke?
Mmm-hmm.

02:55.109 --> 02:56.842
That's not even a thing!

02:56.844 --> 02:57.876
You can see this movie.

02:57.878 --> 02:59.111
ADAM:  <i>"The Great Mouse</i>
<i>Detective?"</i>

02:59.113 --> 03:01.413
(SINGSONGY)
He's got a little
magnifying glass.

03:01.415 --> 03:03.382
Ooh, take Pops.
He loves talking animals.

03:03.384 --> 03:08.487
And here is
a little extra money
for something sweet.

03:08.555 --> 03:10.756
Now how about a little
somethin' sweet for me?

