Mom, do we have to do this
every morning?

03:13.526 --> 03:15.861
It's been four days
since I've gotten a huggie.

03:15.863 --> 03:18.664
I'm jonesin'.
I need my fix.

03:18.666 --> 03:20.299
(CHUCKLES)

03:20.301 --> 03:22.434
Ooh...

03:22.869 --> 03:24.736
What are you doing?
What is this?

03:24.738 --> 03:25.537
You wanted a hug.

03:25.539 --> 03:28.574
Who hugs like that?
At least put some arm
into it.

03:28.576 --> 03:31.210
This is what I got.
Oh...

03:32.045 --> 03:32.511
Go.

03:32.513 --> 03:35.247
<i>Even though my mom</i>
<i>was being denied</i>
<i>the affection she wanted,</i>

03:35.249 --> 03:38.517
<i>I wasn't about to be denied</i>
Poltergeist.

03:38.519 --> 03:40.586
Thanks again
for bringing me.

03:40.588 --> 03:41.286
Of course.

03:41.288 --> 03:45.791
Popcorn, milk duds,
a Mouse Detective...

03:45.793 --> 03:47.025
What's not to like?

03:47.027 --> 03:49.795
Um...
(DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING)

03:49.862 --> 03:52.531
